{"tid":2378111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯校市集擅自移師BigBigShop，變相強迫學生同TVB合作","createTime":"2021-01-24T07:49:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T10:01:08.000Z","uid":255624,"like":259,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"d56a66843b499edd65d95d1ef0bb0f2ad40b3746","tid":2378111,"uid":255624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:49:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdxWSqu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsdxWSqu.jpg&h=2f72d80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n懶人包：<br />\n1️⃣ 有個聯校活動叫做「趁墟做老闆」，畀學生學吓做生意，主辦單位係九龍倉旗下基金。<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ 由於疫情關係，「趁墟」上年停辦咗，今年九龍倉決定將聯校市集改為網上進行，而九龍倉就選擇咗用TVB嘅網購平台BigBigShop。<br />\n<br />\n3️⃣ 九龍倉事前未有諮詢校方，變相係強迫老師、學生同TVB合作。<br />\n<br />\n4️⃣ 參加咗嘅學校需要向TVB繳納15%銷售收益以及存倉費，校方亦需要自行將商品送到BBS倉庫。<br />\n<br />\n5️⃣ 九龍倉解釋，搵TVB係因為可以借助佢哋已有嘅「顧客群」，此外，活動獲得TVB支持，所以已經豁免咗年費同上架費。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">【派嬲質詢任務😡】</span></span></strong><br />\n學校起動計劃 (九龍倉)<br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/292777084158243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F292777084158243&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=01c62fb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/292777084158243</a></p>"},{"pid":"a6d50d37f4535f5db7275447962fcf193bfa2a8c","tid":2378111,"uid":255624,"like":54,"dislike":3,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:49:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210124/LLG2CJR7Z5BDNHDA7EJOSDJDHQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210124%2FLLG2CJR7Z5BDNHDA7EJOSDJDHQ%2F&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=d82aa7c4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210124%2FLLG2CJR7Z5BDNHDA7EJOSDJDHQ%2F&h=3b2b3433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210124/LLG2CJR7Z5BDNHDA7EJOSDJDHQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n有參與學校的老師透露，基金從未就上述活動與TVB合作一事向學校諮詢；由於今年活動首次改為網店形式，故不肯定學校須否如以往般預先墊支相關費用。他又質疑，活動變相強迫學生與TVB合作，亦間接為其宣傳及增加網站流量，而不論參與學校盈虧與否，TVB亦能從活動中賺取上述費用。"},{"pid":"8c729af1f59f656baa87ff51247e28d625c60f08","tid":2378111,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:49:35.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d459af133171c3e35c82a4399e6f14664ca6bb","tid":2378111,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77c78cb694dddf426cd5f3dca3e6b6b45b6d298","tid":2378111,"uid":115752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:50:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9409e3a765807848d028038581b3c72e68ef089","tid":2378111,"uid":255624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:52:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6a6d24cd71225f1693a7f2ba3083ec7e54a7b4","tid":2378111,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:52:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b5e03097aec39409fa6f503c7ce0b98e01dd7b","tid":2378111,"uid":64337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\