九龍倉旗下基金。<br />\n<br />\n2️⃣ 由於疫情關係，「趁墟」上年停辦咗，今年九龍倉決定將聯校市集改為網上進行，而九龍倉就選擇咗用TVB嘅網購平台BigBigShop。<br />\n<br />\n3️⃣ 九龍倉事前未有諮詢校方，變相係強迫老師、學生同TVB合作。<br />\n<br />\n4️⃣ 參加咗嘅學校需要向TVB繳納15%銷售收益以及存倉費，校方亦需要自行將商品送到BBS倉庫。<br />\n<br />\n5️⃣ 九龍倉解釋，搵TVB係因為可以借助佢哋已有嘅「顧客群」，此外，活動獲得TVB支持，所以已經豁免咗年費同上架費。<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"center\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">【派嬲質詢任務😡】</span></span></strong><br />\n學校起動計劃 (九龍倉)<br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/292777084158243\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.sopili.net%2Fl%2Ffacebook%2Fpage%2F292777084158243&d=phsggM5TdZzYtR7qgPv%2BCEPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=01c62fb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.sopili.net/l/facebook/page/292777084158243</a></p>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:35:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"405e171d70a06791333d615b8819f6b100bbc778","tid":2378111,"uid":13448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:44:05.000Z","msg":"咁賣唔出tvb就無錢分<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n校方學生局住照跟唔每代表消費者要受<br />\n幫佢大力宣傳下 不過係罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05f00ce3c36ce6607fc6fd970bfb9e63de062f8e","tid":2378111,"uid":53122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:50:35.000Z","msg":"向每間參與學校校監查問有無得佢同意"},{"pid":"97b45a5c201472d97413301cf189b69683231805","tid":2378111,"uid":125026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:51:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bc505e035d7f3675ac266841ead9da5fc26511c","tid":2378111,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:52:14.000Z","msg":"呢壇嘢lose lose , 仲想食人15%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a0053b015e1115fc0a5bfbec1f9e28f26940d2","tid":2378111,"uid":254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-24T09:52:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"663ed6c90cedd66b779d811e1d4d2da0590997